      "published_date": "2026-07-17T07:53:02+00:00",
      "category": "Industry",
      "description": "NVIDIA released Nemotron 3 Embed on July 15 and 16, 2026. The collection has three open checkpoints: Nemotron-3-Embed-8B-BF16, Nemotron-3-Embed-1B-BF16, and Nemotron-3-Embed-1B-NVFP4. The 8B ranks #1 on RTEB at 78.46 average NDCG@10. The 1B came from ModelOpt NAS pruning plus COS+MSE distillation from the 8B teacher. NVFP4 retains 99%+ of BF16 retrieval accuracy at up to 2x Blackwell throughput. All three run 32,768-token inputs under OpenMDW-1.1. The post NVIDIA AI Releases Nemotron 3 Embed:...",
